No. 574,

October Term, 1963.

Williamson et al., Executors v. Peurifoy, Judge.

C. A. 5th Cir. Second motion to recall and amend order of this Court of January 6, 1964, denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 386 U. S. 901.]
